Mike Armstrong reports from the streets of Washington, D.C., which has been locked down in the leadup to the inauguration. Mercedes Stephenson has reaction from the Trudeau government. Canadian provinces each have their own timeline for vaccinating seniors who don‚Äôt live in long-term care or retirement homes against COVID-19.
